WEBVTT

00:01:29.240 --> 00:01:32.056
CSR is the norm today,

00:01:32.080 --> 00:01:33.480
and it's very useful.

00:01:34.000 --> 00:01:37.056
It provides a route
for corporate generosity

00:01:37.080 --> 00:01:41.056
and that generosity is important
to many corporations' employees

00:01:41.080 --> 00:01:42.280
and customers.

00:01:43.520 --> 00:01:44.776
But you know what?

00:01:44.800 --> 00:01:46.376
It's just not big enough,

00:01:46.400 --> 00:01:47.616
or strong enough,

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:49.176
or durable enough

00:01:49.200 --> 00:01:53.536
to drive solutions to the biggest
problems in our world today

00:01:53.560 --> 00:01:55.720
because it's incremental cost.

00:01:57.520 --> 00:01:59.360
Even when business is booming,